    <span class="h1 enlighten">How to avoid <b>frozen and burst pipes</b></span>
  </h1>
  <p slot="paragraph"><span style="color: red;">Please reduce content here</span></p>
  <p slot="paragraph">As those winter months set in and temperatures plummet, it’s worth keeping a close eye on your home’s water pipes.</p>
  <p slot="paragraph">Because if one of your inlet pipes were to freeze over, there’s a high chance it could also burst.</p>
  <p slot="paragraph">At best you’ll face disruption and the cost of repairs. At worst? We could be talking thousands of pounds worth of flooding damage.</p>
  <p slot="paragraph">But fear not – for a little pre-winter prep can help you keep those frozen pipes at bay…</p>
</ns-landmark>

