    <h2 slot="heading">
      <span class="h5">How to avoid frozen and burst pipes.</span>
      <span class="h1 enlighten">Remind yourself <b>where your stopcock is</b></span>
    </h2>
    <div slot="paragraph">
        <p>It’s essential that you know how to stop the water flow to your home in case the worst happens.</p>
        <p>So familiarise yourself with the location of your stopcock, clear the area around it for easy access, and use it immediately if you spot a leaky pipe!</p>
    </div>
